# Overrides the deep child via `parent.inner` (the with-extracted alias).
# Because `parent.inner` and `parent.mid.inner` resolve to the same
# EvalInstanceKey, the overlay is observable through both aliases — `direct`
# reads it via the alias, while `via_mid` and `doubled_mid` reach the same
# instance through `mid`.
design parent

value.inner = 99
